message: "They unfortunately come out of the woodwork every time we do this," ASAC DeWitt said. "This monster will bring a child and will sell them into the sex slave industry. Our goal is to recover that child and provide them with physical and emotional resources that we can in the FBI," DeWitt said.

data.description: Operation Cross Country targets sex traffickers in an undercover FBI operation.
data.title: FBI's Operation Cross Country arrests sex traffickers and saves children, including kids in the metro
